 a\nconstructive algorithm that is suitable for computer implementation and give\nseveral applications, including contextualizing several results in the theory\nof classical (analytic) splines.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 5 Aug 2021 17:43:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 15 May 2023 09:47:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-16"}
