-the-art approaches are to an application in clinical\npractice and how active this research field is, taking into account the number\nof publications, datasets and challenges.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 6 Aug 2021 08:18:28 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 3 Apr 2023 06:41:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-04"}
