th high precision are approximately the same.\nTherefore, one can conclude that at a given hard scale, the LO approximation is\ngood enough for calculating the EMC ratios of light nuclei.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 6 Aug 2021 12:15:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-09"}
